{"tid":824085,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"個個都話加菲仔做Spider-Man做得好，其實做文戲佢都好出色","createTime":"2018-09-17T03:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T00:03:02.000Z","uid":74778,"like":17,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0c14fdd6260dcd7b043a4bb3ce1d95d889c5e391","tid":824085,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T03:00:42.000Z","msg":"Martin Scorsese 用加菲仔拍遠藤周作既&lt;沉默&gt;真係正到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/100452_5036804e15b17947e6d40fdb159ac6a2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F100452_5036804e15b17947e6d40fdb159ac6a2.png&h=a4904e73&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/100453_d6672c8e3f67818481c2e55487a5fddf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F100453_d6672c8e3f67818481c2e55487a5fddf.png&h=521722e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n靚仔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/103403_133b85ff20ef32f5ac82f348ca2190be.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F103403_133b85ff20ef32f5ac82f348ca2190be.gif&h=d38ac76a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nOscar 最佳攝影真係唔講得小，好多都係用定鏡拍，個鏡頭好少會移動，有d對話會多分鏡，斬到好碎，不過咁樣會更似一本小說<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/103725_1994d4439197106ef045d551b910109b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F103725_1994d4439197106ef045d551b910109b.png&h=e5e18d6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n窪塚洋介<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/101020_2cbc9152ed97a39cab71f739c8a84f03.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F101020_2cbc9152ed97a39cab71f739c8a84f03.png&h=a187d786&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSpider-man同黑武士都係神父，要去日本搵返自己恩師，不過果陣日本政府對基督教進行緊迫害，為左杜絕基督教係日本既根，佢要d外國神父係佢d日本人教徒面前棄教，否則唔係皮肉上既折磨，係精神上，即係係佢地面前殺害同折磨佢既日本人教徒。最後qui gon jinn 同Spider-man係棄教加做埋日本人，黑武士就係教日本教徒之中死左。不過棄教後，Spider-man個樣明顯變得非常空洞虛無<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LXmubA7z_Ew\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLXmubA7z_Ew&d=GWino2b2s9Yv%2Fj0LkwBpOAHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=9ed2274d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LXmubA7z_Ew</a><br />\n個攝影好好，好有感染力，加菲仔既信念崩潰，令人都好崩潰，好沈重。<br />\n<br />\nMartin既沈默係一套完全無味精既電影，用既係演技同攝影，演員好清楚自己個情感要去到邊。日本演員演一個對西方宗教咁瘋狂既人真係好勁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/103801_c613bfc8859ae607af5ec354eb467cbb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F103801_c613bfc8859ae607af5ec354eb467cbb.png&h=793e355c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加菲仔就唔係一味咁衝動同倔強，佢睇住黑武士死果幕個無奈無助樣真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EAQBr9ULYG4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEAQBr9ULYG4&d=GWino2b2s9Yv%2Fj0LkwBpOAHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=d562f8bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EAQBr9ULYG4</a><br />\n<br />\n佢真係做左個，企係罪人同耶穌基督之間既神父。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/103824_7834fccd35a6984720fb4d1b30a2eda4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F103824_7834fccd35a6984720fb4d1b30a2eda4.png&h=30d9d328&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/103826_0a00a1ed151883bb1017e527da5f5b5d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F103826_0a00a1ed151883bb1017e527da5f5b5d.png&h=1e42bca5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/103827_83e8abba8f3e38b28323920f6a2e204c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F103827_83e8abba8f3e38b28323920f6a2e204c.png&h=efc087d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔能夠話&lt;沈默&gt;係martin想講想表達既野，因為佢係改編自遠藤周作既&lt;沈默&gt;，而&lt;沈默&gt;係遠藤既三部曲之首，我睇過佢第二部既&lt;武士&gt;，講既野係好似，不過係日本人，去左異地被迫仲主，回國後被視為叛國，被處死既悲劇。當中有一段對話好似qui gon jinn 同Spider-man係&lt;沈默&gt;入面最後既辯論<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n<em> 「日本人&hellip;是在這世界裡最不適合我們信仰的人&hellip; 因為日本人本質上，對於超越人的絕對性﹑超越自然的存在，以及我們稱為超自然的東西並無感覺&hellip; 然而，可怕的是日本人有享受這世界無常的能力。由於這能力足夠，因此他們享受停留的樂趣&hellip; 他們的感性經常停留在自然的次元，絕不再提升。在自然的次元中，那種感性微妙﹑精緻得令人吃驚&hellip; 因此，日本人無法了解與人不同次元的我們的神。」《武士》</em></span><br />\n<br />\n遠藤周作係由一個日本人既角度去睇宗教信仰，亦都係由基督教去睇日本，而Martin係毫無刪改加減地將小說呈現係電影上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deaeff2dfaa874c14958170dc98f128592e53c58","tid":824085,"uid":190789,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T03:04:22.000Z","msg":"呢套好睇<br />\n<br />\n蜘蛛仔拍戲好睇，佢係唔係信耶蘇？佢拍多耶片"},{"pid":"86cddb134edef4cfe35224722e55a18d8c5ee453","tid":824085,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T04:53:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"147bbd4e55e52a83cacb4899a436ea2589516365","tid":824085,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T05:28:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d38d2adcb4bed099e8b334479543841a4c2ef0","tid":824085,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T06:22:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e1e4d7ebd2aba7815eb1b8c3276649bf6f22155","tid":824085,"uid":27324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"deaeff2dfaa874c14958170dc98f128592e53c58","tid":824085,"uid":190789,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1